3FCj6m&quot;>;毫无疑问，马斯克控制着这辆车：他是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/28/23848882/elon -musk-tesla-fsd-v12-demo-red-light-zuckerberg-house&quot;>;被迫停止他的“全面...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2023/8/28/23850011/elon-musk-driven-phone-california-law-palo-alto&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/28/23850011/elon-musk-driving-phone-california-law-palo-alto" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/28/23850011/elon-musk-driven-phone-california-law-palo-alto</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry></feed>